    • Constructor Detail

      • QuasiRoot

        public QuasiRoot(int width,
                 int height)
        Create a new root interface to the graphic element hierarchy. This is meant to serve as a bridge between some other graphic library. The position will be 0,0 as this is the root - there's really no other option.
        Parameters:
        width - The width of the graphic interface
        height - The height of the graphic interface
